[[珍妮佛·勞倫斯|珍妮佛·勞倫斯]]原本打算扮演欧菲，但因档期冲突放弃<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming|first=Mike|title=Oscar Nominee Jennifer Lawrence In Talks For Oliver Stone's 'Savages'|url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/02/oscar-nominee-jennifer-lawrence-to-star-in-oliver-stones-savages/|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2012-04-19|date=2011-02-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120529050026/http://www.deadline.com/2011/02/oscar-nominee-jennifer-lawrence-to-star-in-oliver-stones-savages/|archivedate=2012-05-29}}</ref>。其他代替劳伦斯的人选包括[[艾梅柏·希爾德|艾梅柏·希爾德]]、[[奧利維亞·魏爾德|奧利維亞·魏爾德]]、[[泰莉莎·柏爾馬|泰莉莎·柏爾馬]]和[[艾比·柯尼施|艾比·柯尼施]]<ref>{{cite web|last=Jaugernauth|first=Kevin|title=Blake Lively, Abbie Cornish & Teresa Palmer Reading For Oliver Stone's 'Savages'; Uni Picks Up Film|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/blake_lively_teresa_palmer_reading_for_oliver_stones_savages_universal|work=IndieWire|accessdate=2012-04-19|date=2011-03-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605065307/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/blake_lively_teresa_palmer_reading_for_oliver_stones_savages_universal|archivedate=2013-06-05}}</ref>。2011年4月，据报道[[布蕾克·萊芙莉|布蕾克·萊芙莉]]被选为欧菲的扮演者<ref>{{cite web|last=Bettinger|first=Brendan|title=Blake Lively, John Travolta, and Uma Thurman Join Taylor Kitsch and Aaron Johnson SAVAGES|url=http://collider.com/blake-lively-john-travolta-uma-thurman-savages/87189/|publisher=Collider.com|accessdate=2012-04-19|date=2011-04-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120418131852/http://collider.com/blake-lively-john-travolta-uma-thurman-savages/87189/|archivedate=2012-04-18}}</ref>。在泰勒·克奇加盟前，奥利弗·斯通让导演[[彼得·柏格|彼得·柏格]]给他看克奇在《[[超級戰艦|超級戰艦]]》中的30分钟片段，看他是如何扮演男一号的，阅毕便录用他<ref>{{cite web|title=Taylor Kitsch: His Make-Or-Break Year|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20574711_2,00.html|work=Entertainment Weekly|publisher=Time Inc|accessdate=2012-04-19|author=Adam B. Vary|page=2|date=2012-02-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131003050503/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20574711_2,00.html|archivedate=2013-10-03}}</ref>。[[特萊沃·多諾萬|特萊沃·多諾萬]]原本为角色试镜，但看过多诺万的录像后，他被拿掉，因为斯通指出他的角色原著没有<ref>{{cite web|last=Malkin|first=Marc|title=Oliver Stone Wrote a Part in His New Movie for Who? (Hint: A 90210 Star!)|url=http://uk.eonline.com/news/marc_malkin/oliver_stone_wrote_part_in_his_new/311021|work=E! Online|publisher=NBC Universal|accessdate=2012-05-26|date=2012-04-23}}{{Dead link|date=2019年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。[[乌玛·瑟曼|乌玛·瑟曼]]饰演了奥菲的母亲帕夸，考虑到时长，她的戏份被剪光<ref>{{cite web|title=Oliver Stone, 'Savages' Director, On Graphic Sex Scenes, The War On Drugs And Barack Obama|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/06/20/oliver-stone-savages-war-on-drugs_n_1613496.html|work=Huffington Post|publisher=AOL|accessdate=2012-06-20|author=Michael Hogan|date=2012-06-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120621075011/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/06/20/oliver-stone-savages-war-on-drugs_n_1613496.html|archivedate=2012-06-21}}</ref>。

